data.description: A great location, close to schools, and a short distance to shopping centers and restaurants. A great spacious condo with 3 bedrooms, and 2 full baths, the home has new neutral paint, and new carpet throughout the unit. Walk into a small foyer, with a separate dining room, an enclosed kitchen, and a very large and bright living room, walk out to the balcony. The Master bedroom with its a separate full bathroom, 2 bedrooms with a shared full bathroom, and plenty of closet space.
